node.text: Don’t let yourself lose faith in your dreams and goals. Whatever you’ve been through, remember you made it this far, don’t let it be for nothing. You’ve got this!

node.text: Control them (your emotions) or they control you.

node.text: Believe it! And never stop working for it. Comment “Yes” if you receive it.
